  <summary>5/8/1996--Introduced.
Persian Gulf Syndrome Health Benefits Extension Act of 1996 - Authorizes the Secretary of Veterans Affairs to extend priority health care to veterans exposed to a toxic substance or environmental hazard while serving in Israel or Turkey during the Persian Gulf War.</summary>
